1793
01:24:59.426 --> 01:25:01.293
-Uh-huh.
-You're the king of marketing.

1794
01:25:01.428 --> 01:25:04.030
You know. I just. uh.
I think that you and I.

1795
01:25:04.166 --> 01:25:06.298
if we came together.
we could. uh...

1796
01:25:07.499 --> 01:25:09.030
