<i> (dramatic music playing on TV)</i>

1823
01:26:20.337 --> 01:26:21.969
(Katherine laughing)

1824
01:26:22.104 --> 01:26:24.640
Now. that... now. that's
my favorite part. (laughs)

1825
01:26:30.682 --> 01:26:32.511
I'm gonna
leave it to you. Michael.

1826
01:26:32.646 --> 01:26:33.845
You can't go yet.

1827
01:26:33.981 --> 01:26:35.719
No.
I'm going to bed. I'm tired.

1828
01:26:35.855 --> 01:26:37.220
You got to stay for the ending.
That's the best part.

1829
01:26:37.355 --> 01:26:39.560
Your mother is tired. baby.

1830
