-Here we go.

1857
01:28:15.753 --> 01:28:17.951
I have to start
living my own life.

1858
01:28:19.322 --> 01:28:21.119
On my own.

1859
01:28:21.964 --> 01:28:23.690
Just like everyone else.

1860
01:28:23.825 --> 01:28:25.761
You ain't like everyone else.

1861
01:28:27.433 --> 01:28:29.126
So. you're trying to tell me

1862
01:28:29.261 --> 01:28:31.635
you want to be treated
like an adult?

1863
01:28:32.500 --> 01:28:33.934
All right.

1864
01:28:34.069 --> 01:28:37.809
You want to
see what the world is like...

1865
01:28:38.579 --> 01:28:41.210
...without a family
that protects you.

1866
01:28:41.345 --> 01:28:42.772
(hinges creaking)

1867
01:28:42.908 --> 01:28:45.015
Without a family that...

1868
01:28:45.150 --> 01:28:46.719
understands you.

1869
01:28:47.655 --> 01:28:50.821
Nobody else will understand you
outside this place.

1870
01:28:50.956 --> 01:28:53.920
There you'll be with
all the money in the world.

1871
01:28:54.055 --> 01:28:56.620
surrounded by people
who'll say "yes"

1872
01:28:56.756 --> 01:28:59.157
to everything.

1873
01:29:00.794 --> 01:29:03.161
Is that what you want?

1874
01:29:06.406 --> 01:29:08.342
What kind of sense that make?

1875
01:29:15.577 --> 01:29:17.883
I'm gonna...

1876
01:29:18.019 --> 01:29:19.616
call Don King

1877
01:29:19.752 --> 01:29:22.312
and tell him
you're doing the tour.

1878
01:29:24.285 --> 01:29:26.987
I know you don't want
to let your family down.

1879
01:29:29.626 --> 01:29:31.860
(Michael breathing deeply)

1880
