1884
01:29:50.910 --> 01:29:53.684
("Billie Jean" playing)

1885
01:29:57.954 --> 01:30:00.184
♪ You're a whole
new generation ♪

1886
01:30:00.320 --> 01:30:02.327
♪ You're lovin' what you do ♪

1887
01:30:02.463 --> 01:30:04.354
♪ Put a Pepsi in the motion ♪

1888
01:30:04.489 --> 01:30:06.327
♪ That choice is up to you.
hey-ey ♪

1889
01:30:06.462 --> 01:30:08.326
-DIRECTOR: Cut! Cut! Cut! Cut!
-♪ You're the Pepsi... ♪

1890
