that will grow back.

1972
01:33:45.612 --> 01:33:48.853
You'll need surgery
to laser the scar tissue

1973
01:33:48.988 --> 01:33:51.851
and stretch part of the scalp
over the burn.

1974
01:33:52.654 --> 01:33:55.690
All right? We'll insert
an implant
to protect the scalp.

1975
01:33:55.826 --> 01:33:57.824
Will I have to wear a wig?

1976
01:33:57.960 --> 01:33:59.930
Well. right there on top.

1977
01:34:01.967 --> 01:34:04.433
What kind of wig?
Like. a full wig?

1978
01:34:04.568 --> 01:34:06.002
Hard to say.

1979
01:34:06.137 --> 01:34:08.074
There are prosthetic
hair weaves we can try.

1980
01:34:08.209 --> 01:34:11.469
but we won't know till we see
how the surgery goes next week.

1981
01:34:13.977 --> 01:34:16.276
(indistinct P.A. announcement)

1982
01:34:17.918 --> 01:34:19.449
(crowd shouting indistinctly
in the distance)

1983
01:34:19.584 --> 01:34:21.184
You'll. um...

1984
01:34:21.319 --> 01:34:23.786
you'll have to stay
on the Demerol for a while.

1985
01:34:23.922 --> 01:34:25.756
I don't want
to take medication.

1986
01:34:25.892 --> 01:34:27.788
I have to be honest.
Mr. Jackson.

1987
01:34:27.924 --> 01:34:29.427
you're gonna need them.

1988
01:34:29.997 --> 01:34:32.289
We have to replace
the implant periodically.

1989
01:34:32.424 --> 01:34:34.401
The nerves
are exposed up there.

1990
01:34:34.536 --> 01:34:36.527
You'll be in a lot of pain.

1991
01:34:39.039 --> 01:34:42.038
I'll let you rest.
but I'll be back later.

1992
01:34:47.479 --> 01:34:50.045
WOMAN: We'll stay here
till you're better. Michael!

1993
01:34:50.181 --> 01:34:51.642
