You see the number of people

1994
01:34:51.777 --> 01:34:53.881
who have already gathered
outside the hospital.

1995
01:34:54.017 --> 01:34:55.248
If that isn't a testament

1996
01:34:55.384 --> 01:34:56.982
to the star power
of Michael Jackson.

1997
01:34:57.118 --> 01:34:58.750
I don't know what is.

1998
01:34:58.885 --> 01:35:00.692
...say they won't go back
until Jackson is all right.

1999
01:35:00.828 --> 01:35:02.861
-(donkey braying on TV)
