Got all your favorites.

2003
01:35:08.463 --> 01:35:09.835
-Golden Temple...
-(Katherine laughs)

2004
01:35:09.970 --> 01:35:11.330
-they send their love.
-Golden Temple's

2005
01:35:11.466 --> 01:35:12.537
-your favorite. Michael.
