2006
01:35:12.672 --> 01:35:14.070
Chinese. Some fried chicken.

2007
01:35:14.205 --> 01:35:16.204
Even got these
little red candies you like.

2008
01:35:17.312 --> 01:35:18.675
Thanks. Bill.

2009
01:35:18.810 --> 01:35:20.807
You can just leave it there.

2010
01:35:20.942 --> 01:35:22.507
I'm not hungry.

2011
01:35:23.218 --> 01:35:25.378
Oh. Okay.

2012
01:35:28.117 --> 01:35:29.687
I'll leave you all to it.

2013
01:35:29.823 --> 01:35:32.825
-Okay. Thank you. Bill.
-Mm-hmm.

2014
01:35:40.995 --> 01:35:43.136
(door closes)

2015
01:35:43.271 --> 01:35:45.101
