2018
01:36:09.426 --> 01:36:13.690
Mother. I don't want to
discuss this right now.

2019
01:36:14.499 --> 01:36:16.066
Okay.

2020
01:36:16.931 --> 01:36:18.805
(monitor beeps)

2021
01:36:21.905 --> 01:36:24.074
No one can stop Joseph.

2022
01:36:27.512 --> 01:36:29.112
Nobody.

2023
01:36:37.090 --> 01:36:39.856
You just know that.
no matter what happens.

2024
01:36:39.991 --> 01:36:42.653
I'm gonna be here for you...

2025
01:36:43.463 --> 01:36:45.359
...always.

2026
01:36:47.968 --> 01:36:50.034
I should get
some rest now. Mother.

2027
01:37:02.009 --> 01:37:04.345
